<span id="user" style="float:right;"><a href="//u.sanwen.net/connect/qqlogin" rel="nofollow">会员登陆 &amp; 注册</a></span></div></div><div id="header"><div class="site"><div class="logo"><a href="/"><img src="//i0.sanwen.net/images/xlogo.png" alt="返回中国散文网首页"></a></div><div class="search"><form action="/dosearch" method="post" target="_blank"><button id="sbtnsearch"></button><input name="keywords" type="text" class="txt" placeholder="搜索文章"></form></div></div><div class="nav"><a href="http://m.sanwen.net/" target="_blank" style="float:right;">手机站</a><a href="/" class="on">首页<em></em></a><a href="/sanwen/">散文<em></em></a><a href="/shige/">诗歌<em></em></a><a href="/zawen/">杂文<em></em></a><a href="/suibi/">随笔<em></em></a><a href="/rizhi/">日记<em></em></a><a href="/novel/">小小说<em></em></a></div><div class="subnav"><a href="//www.sanwen.net/" class="path_home">散文网</a> » <a href="/sanwen/">经典散文</a> »<a href="/sanwen/qingmingjie/">清明节散文</a> » 清明雨</div></div><!--/#header--><div id="content"><div id="main"><div id="article"><div class="title"><h1 style="color:red;"><i class="c"></i>清明雨</h1></div><div class="info">2016-04-06 23:33&nbsp;作者:<a href="//u.sanwen.net/555333.html" target="_blank">茫茫人海</a>&nbsp;<label><span id="article_click">868</span>人读过</label>&nbsp;|&nbsp;19条评论&nbsp;<a href="/related/3829241/" target="_blank" title="清明雨的相关文章">相关文章</a> | <a href="//u.sanwen.net/manage/articleadd" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">我要投稿</a></div><div class="content"><div class="adcontent"><script>_get_content_ad();</script><script async="" src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script><!-- sw_336_280_zw --><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:inline-block;width:336px;height:280px" data-ad-client="ca-pub-1637650971853106" data-ad-slot="4858989558" data-adsbygoogle-status="done"><ins id="aswift_0_expand" style="display:inline-table;border:none;height:280px;margin:0;padding:0;position:relative;visibility:visible;width:336px;background-color:transparent"><ins id="aswif